Subject: [PATCH 0861/5242] MLK-12284-2 doc: syscon: add clocks as optional
 property

commit  ce24908a49c90518a80f47cca9e3ad5f8ebdbaed from
https://source.codeaurora.org/external/imx/linux-imx.git

User can specify clocks in devicetree which is used for accessing the registers
in this regmap.

